          <Dots class="mb-4" />
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
            <span class="text-xl">üîπ</span> Explore the Outdoors of Granada on your
            MTB through an area with many landscapes from rolling hills, pine forests,
            deserts, and mountains to the tropical coast.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
            <span class="text-xl">üîπ</span>Enjoy our rural hotel selected with
            great care for its location and character to make your trip a single
            experience.
