            class="max-w-2xl md:px-0 font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">
            MTB
          </h2>
          <Dots class="mb-4" />
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Check our BLOG CYCLING article ‚ÄúOur Bicycle Selection‚Äù to see your
            MTB. We provide 2 high-quality mountain bikes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
            <span class="text-xl">üîπ</span> When booking, you indicate your height
            and weight to have the correct frame size of the bicycle at the start
            of your tour.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
            <span class="text-xl">üîπ</span> We facilitate fitting your pedals or
            saddle if you wish to bring them.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
            <span class="text-xl">üîπ</span> We provide low-range gearing suited to
            mountainous terrain
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
            <span class="text-xl">üîπ</span> We provide spare parts and take care
            of the day-to-day maintenance during the tour.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Button to download PDF -->
      <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-12">
        <div class="grid">
          <div>
            <h2 class="md:px-0 font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">
              Cancellation Policy
            </h2>
            <Dots class="mb-4" />
