          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="">
          <h2
            class="max-w-2xl md:px-0 font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">
            Level
          </h2>
          <Dots class="mb-4" />
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-900 mb-2">
            The route type and difficulty are based on your fitness level and
            technical skills. Booking the ‚ÄúMTB Escape Granada‚Äù, we ask you to
            fill out a questionnaire form to tailor your itinerary to the right
